@startuml seq-chaos-g5
title G4 — Séquence : notification + Chaos Monkey (G5 down)

actor Client
participant "NotificationController" as C
participant "G5NotificationClient" as G5
database "pending_notifications" as DB

Client -> C : POST /api/notifications/send
C -> G5 : HTTP (CircuitBreaker)
G5 --> C : échec / timeout
C -> DB : save PENDING
C --> Client : 202 DEGRADED
note right of DB : Retry auto 30s\nou POST /pending-notifications/retry
@enduml
